show.description: Anna becomes CEO Ian’s secret lover to save her boyfriend. Abandoned by Ian, she dates playboy David. Facing heart failure, she meets Ian disguised as K. Her amnesiac boyfriend Louis returns, manipulated by Annetta. Rescued by crime lord Domenico and forced to marry him, Anna is later kidnapped. Ian and Louis team up to save her, revealing Ian’s true feelings. Amid dark secrets, Anna navigates four men’s obsessions to find true love.
